    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> deux variables aléatoires réelles et soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span> deux paramètres réels tels que la loi du couple <span class=\"math inline\">\\((X,Y)\\)</span> soit donnée par le tableau joint:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(X \\backslash Y\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(-1\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(-2\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{6}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{2}{18}\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(-1\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{9}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(2\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{18}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{2}{6}\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Quelle est la valeur du paramètre <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>On a nécessairement: <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\frac{1}{6}+\\frac{2}{18}+\\frac{1}{9}+ a +\\frac{1}{18}+\\frac{2}{6}=1\\]</span> donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a=\\frac{2}{9}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
