    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>L’espérance de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> est la suivante: <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n        \\E(X)&amp;= (-2)\\prob(X=-2)+(-1)\\prob(X=-1)+1\\prob(X=1)+2\\prob(X=2) \\\\\n        &amp;= (-2)\\times \\frac{5}{18}+(-1) \\frac{2}{18}+\\frac{4}{18}+2\\times \\frac{7}{18} \\\\\n        &amp;=\\frac{1}{3}.\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span> L’espérance de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> est <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n        \\E(Y)&amp;= (-1)\\prob(Y=-1)+y\\prob(Y=-y) \\\\\n        &amp;= (-1)\\times \\frac{6}{18}+y\\times \\frac{12}{18} \\\\\n        &amp;=\\frac{-1}{3}+\\frac{2}{3}y.\n        \\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
